description: Remove a label or labels from a parameter.

parameters.name: Name
parameters.description: The name of the parameter from which you want to delete one or more labels.

parameters.name: ParameterVersion
parameters.description: The specific version of the parameter which you want to delete one or more labels from. If it isn't present, the call will fail.

parameters.name: Labels
parameters.description: One or more labels to delete from the specified parameter version. (string) ---

nested_items.name: RemovedLabels
nested_items.description: A list of all labels deleted from the parameter.

nested_items.name: InvalidLabels
nested_items.description: The labels that aren't attached to the given parameter version.
